content: Reads for me while I listen. Can go through more chapters in a day than by manually reading. Only problem is: l can't highlight selected texts. Bummer.
Excellent I love it so enjoyable to listen to

I couldn't download this app at first, so what I did was delete the free version, turn off parental controls (from GPlay settings), force stop GPlay app (from phone settings), and then restart my phone. Problem solved. I hope this helps.
It won't play after you purchase. Buyer beware.
I love the reading of the word and the MSG Bible very clear no computer sound

I really love this app. Absolutely loved being able to speed up or slow down the audio. Also loved how the reader would keep up with audio. Would like a function to allow you to loop chapters and books as I like to listen to passages over and over again. Also would to get this same app in nkjv.

Of course I read several versions of the Bible but this is the one that I 
really enjoy. I like it for my daughter and for other people who might not 
be in love with how the language is in other versions. This is easy to 
follow and makes you WANT to read the holy book. Great job!

This bible app just works perfectly, I'm loving the new bookmark facility. 
Good narrative. Easy to use. Marvellous.
I like the simplicity of the book and layout.
Good app crashes on the odd occasion  using moto z play phone. But great for the Price of $5.50
